{"id":126646,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":12,"day":13}],"page":"9","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"152","ytitle":"","mtitle":"风暴","ftitle":"","authors":["陈孜宁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈孜宁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴正在卷来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在卷来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当月光下谁叩着船舷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说九月的海水太平静了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中也有一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫的水和天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在遥远的水天的一线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永系着对于陌生事物的焦渴的怀念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，洁白的水鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不倦于云彩和波涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让生命(那独自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暗角里饮泣的生命)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也附上你们任一轻快的羽毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去多多地承受阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更以至大的感激"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接一个美丽的风暴。"}]}